{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"iddb191219-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s94"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"94"},"text":"§ 94.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Venue of suits","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Any action or proceeding against a national banking association for which the Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation has been appointed receiver, or against the Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation as receiver of such association, shall be brought in the district or territorial court of the United States held within the district in which that association’s principal place of business is located, or, in the event any State, county, or municipal court has jurisdiction over such an action or proceeding, in such court in the county or city in which that association’s principal place of business is located.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"iddb19121a-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"(R.S. § 5198; ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1875-02-18/ch80/s1"},"text":"Feb. 18, 1875, ch. 80, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/18/320"},"text":"18 Stat. 320","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1911-03-03/ch231/s291"},"text":"Mar. 3, 1911, ch. 231, § 291","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/36/1167"},"text":"36 Stat. 1167","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/320/tIV/s406"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–320, title IV, § 406","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-10-15"},"text":"Oct. 15, 1982","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/96/1512"},"text":"96 Stat. 1512","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/457/s20/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–457, § 20(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1983-01-12"},"text":"Jan. 12, 1983","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/96/2509"},"text":"96 Stat. 2509","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"iddb19121b-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"iddb19121c-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"iddb19121d-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The last sentence of R.S. § 5198, as added by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1875-02-18/ch80/s1"},"text":"act Feb. 18, 1875, ch. 80, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/18/320"},"text":"18 Stat. 320","children":[],"tail":", appears to have been derived from "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1864-06-03/ch106/s57"},"text":"act June 3, 1864, ch. 106, § 57","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/13/116"},"text":"13 Stat. 116","children":[],"tail":", which was the National Bank Act. See "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s38"},"text":"section 38 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section is comprised of last sentence of R.S. § 5198 as added by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1875-02-18/ch80/s1"},"text":"act Feb. 18, 1875, ch. 80, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/18/320"},"text":"18 Stat. 320","children":[],"tail":". The remaining sentences of R.S. § 5198 are classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/u